Write a Python program to Get the name, age and location of a person and display using Multilevel inheritance.

For example:

Input	:
Srinivas
24
chennai

Result : 
Srinivas 24 chennai

INPUT CODE :

# Base class
class Person:
    def get_name(self):
        self.name = input()

# Derived class (Level 2)
class Age(Person):
    def get_age(self):
        self.age = int(input())

# Derived class (Level 3)
class Location(Age):
    def get_location(self):
        self.location = input()
    
    def display(self):
        print(self.name, self.age, self.location)

# Object creation
obj = Location()
obj.get_name()
obj.get_age()
obj.get_location()
obj.display()
